OL,3,CCarlisle pet shop owner says would-be
OL,4,Cthief tried to steal Chihuahua puppy
OL,6,FRicky Pieri told our reporter Kieran
OL,7,FMacfadzean that some of the thieves
OL,8,Fwere people he knew.
OL,10,FA pet shop owner in Carlisle has said
OL,11,Fshoplifting in his store has reached
OL,12,F"disappointing" levels.
OL,14,FRicky Pieri, who has run Nu Pets Pet
OL,15,FCentre in the city for more than 40
OL,16,Fyears, told ITV Border that
OL,17,Fshoplifting has become more frequent
OL,18,Fand severe - with one would-be thief
OL,19,Ftrying to steal a Chihuahua puppy.
