OL,6,FIt comes as Cumbria's Police, Fire and
OL,7,FCrime Commissioner, David Allen, has
OL,8,Fpledged to tackle shoplifting and
OL,9,Fassaults on shop staff in the county
OL,10,Ffollowing national reports that the
OL,11,Fcrime is at an all-time high.
OL,13,FMr Pieri said he has been forced to
OL,14,Fincrease security in his shop to try
OL,15,Fand deter thieves.
OL,17,FHe added: "These were people that have
OL,18,Fbeen coming in shop for years that
OL,19,Fyou've had conversations with and we
OL,20,Fknow them by name.
