OL,6,F"And you find out they're stealing
OL,7,Ffrom you, it's quite heart wrenching.
OL,8,FIt's disappointing."
OL,10,FPositive outcomes where the
OL,11,Fperpetrator of a crime is identified
OL,12,Fand appropriately punished only
OL,13,Foccurred in fewer than 40% of cases
OL,14,Flast year nationwide.
OL,16,FThe most recent crime statistics
OL,17,Freleased by the Office for National
OL,18,FStatistics (ONS) highlight that
OL,19,Fshoplifting figures are at the highest
OL,20,Flevel since records began in 2003.
