OL,3,CCarlisle pet shop owner says would-be
OL,4,Cthief tried to steal Chihuahua puppy
OL,6,FOn Friday 26 July, Cumbria's Police,
OL,7,FFire and Crime Commissioner, David
OL,8,FAllen, pledged to better protect
OL,9,Fbusinesses and their staff.
OL,11,FHe said: "We've seen a 9% rise over
OL,12,Fthe last 12 months, nationally its
OL,13,Fbeen about 17%.
OL,15,F"Lots of reasons for that one of the
OL,16,Freasons is de minimis limit, so lack
OL,17,Fof prosecutions below #200 theft.
OL,19,F"We don't take that approach in
OL,20,Fcumbria we will investigate all the
OL,21,Fcrimes that come to us.
