OL,6,F"Nationally the new government are
OL,7,Fgoing to be bringing in a new act that
OL,8,Fwill get rid of the #200 limit and put
OL,9,Fshop lifting back on the forefront and
OL,10,Falso they'll be specific offences of
OL,11,Fassaulting a shop worker which will
OL,12,Fcarry a mandatory penalty."
OL,14,FHe added they are now making an effort
OL,15,Fto crackdown on shoplifting in the
OL,16,Farea.
