OL,10,Flocal businesses find out what the
OL,11,Fissues are crimes are reported.
OL,13,F"They work with the store keepers to
OL,14,Ftry and find and tackle the prolific
OL,15,Foffenders and the locations where the
OL,16,Foffences are occurring.
